These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, dancing, woodworking, collecting
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, july, june, march
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, rock
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, juice, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, watermelon, broccoli, grapes
 1. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the fan of rock is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person eating grapes##2
 3. the person drinking fanta is the person eating grapes##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person eating asparagus is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the fan of reggae##2
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 7. the person eating watermelon is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
10. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Hobby           | woodworking | hiking   | collecting | dancing |
| Birthday   | november      | july | june              | march |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | funk     | rock               | reggae    |
| Beverage           | lemonade        | juice     | soy-milk           | fanta       |
| Food     | watermelon | broccoli     | asparagus                | grapes      |

