.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, chess, skydiving, drawing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, old-henry, cain, dannemann
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, taxi, van
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, red, emerald, ivory
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 3. the old-henry-smoker is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who likes red##2
 4. the person driving the van is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the person who likes emerald is the old-henry-smoker##1
 6. the cain-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 7. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
10. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Hobby          | skydiving       | chess      | woodworking      | drawing      |
| Cigar           | dannemann | old-henry | cain | baccarat |
| Transport   | van          | subway       | taxi            | jet-ski      |
| Color           | mauve            | emerald    | red           | ivory       |
| Sport         | handball        | sailing    | tennis         | volleyball  |

