There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, juice, lemonade
There are 4 different nationalities: british, colombian, japanese, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, bike, jet-ski, tram
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, december, june, july
 1. the british is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the japanese##1
 4. the person driving the subway is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 7. the british is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person who growszinnia is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the british is the person driving the tram##1
10. the colombian is on the far left##1
11. the colombian is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Flower          | daisy    | bellflower  | balloon-flower | zinnia |
| Beverage   | soy-milk   | juice        | fanta | lemonade     |
