.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, action, fantasy
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, blue, emerald, green
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, house, jazz, pop
4 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, billiard, chess
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, turtle, ferret
 1. the owner of the turtle is the person who likes purple##1
 2. the owner of the frog is between the fan of disco and the fan of house##2
 3. the fan of disco is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person watching action movies is the person playing bridge##1
 5. the fan of house is between the person playing bridge and the owner of the rabbit##2
 6. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 8. the person watching scientific movies is the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is between the owner of the frog and the fan of jazz##2
10. the person who likes green is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Movie-Genre      | fantasy     | time-travel | action    | scientific          |
| Color          | green | purple     | emerald | blue         |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | house       | pop         | disco        |
| Game         | chess  | scrabble     | bridge     | billiard |
| Pet     | rabbit     | turtle      | frog   | ferret          |

