 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of pop is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 7. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 8. the person eating corn is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
10. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person driving the roller##2
11. the fan of trance is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |      4       |
