There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, french, turkish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, epic, documentary, zombie
 1. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 2. the french is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person who likes black is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 6. the turkish is the person who likes black##1
 7. the american is the person who likes fuchsia##1
 8. the person who likes yellow is between the person who likes black and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 9. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person driving the skateboard##2
11. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | july       | november       | february | may    |
