 6. the mechanic is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is between the cottage house and the person drinking water##2
 8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the social-worker##1
 9. the person who likes orange is the entrepreneur##1
10. the person who likes orange is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes light-blue##2
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
12. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |      4      |
