 5. the french is the person traveling to nizza##1
 6. the fan of indie is the owner of the goat##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is the owner of the rabbit##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the right of the french##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left of the japanese##1
11. the japanese is between the person traveling to nizza and the montecristo-smoker##2
12. the argentine is between the fonseca-smoker and the owner of the goat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Pet      | frog      | goat         | rabbit | guinea-pig      |
| City           | nizza | venice | hamburg | miami     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa         | indie          | ambient  | electronic |
| Nationality         | french        | japanese  | argentine | indonesian   |
| Cigar     | ritmeester    | tiparillo         | montecristo     | fonseca     |

