 5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 9. the modern house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person eating peach##1
11. the person eating peach is the person watching adventure movies##1

